title: The Puppy Pitch + Kacey Musgraves Sets Bobby Straight

description:
The show each pitches what kind of puppy Bobby should get. Kacey Musgraves reached out to Bobby on the correct lyrics to her song. Also, Amy ran into Brett Eldredge at the grocery store.
